data.description: Charming Tri-Level Starter Home on Peaceful Cul-de-sac Welcome to your perfect beginning! This inviting three-bedroom, one-bathroom gem nestled on a serene cul-de-sac is the epitome of comfort and convenience.   Key Features: Tri-Level Design: Enjoy the dynamic layout that maximizes space and functionality. This design offers both privacy and togetherness, creating a cozy atmosphere for everyone.    Fresh Updates: A brand-new roof, fresh paint, and plush carpeting throughout mean you can move right in without a worry. No projects needed - just unpack and settle into your new abode!   Peaceful Outdoor Oasis: The spacious yard offers endless opportunities for gardening, play, and relaxation. Create your own sanctuary in this tranquil outdoor space, complete with a fantastic Trex deck for seamless indoor-outdoor living.   Prime Location: Situated close to C-470 and HWY 83 neighborhood, this home is just moments away from parks, schools, and local amenities. Commuting is a breeze with easy access to major thoroughfares.   Shopping and Dining: Explore a wide array of shopping and dining options just a stone's throw away. From local eateries to well-known retailers, everything you need is within reach.  Convenient Parking: The attached garage provides not only shelter for your vehicle but also additional storage space for all your belongings. This is the opportunity you've been waiting for - a move-in ready starter home that combines comfort, style, and convenience. Don't miss out! Schedule your viewing today and make this house your forever home.
